# ppp — Always-on rules

Read [AGENTS.md](mdc:AGENTS.md) before starting any non-trivial task. It contains the session-start template, carry-forward inventory, and decision-log location.

## Stack

- SvelteKit (Svelte 5, runes mode) + TypeScript strict
- Supabase (Postgres + Auth + Edge Functions) — **single hosted project, prod only.** Do not assume or recommend **`supabase start`**, local Docker, or **`supabase db reset`** in this repo unless the user explicitly opts in. Schema: **`npm run supabase:db:push:dry`** then **`npm run supabase:db:push`** to the **CLI-linked** project (run **`npm run supabase:doctor`** if ref/URL drift). Edge Functions: **`npm run supabase:deploy-functions`**. Full commands: [supabase/README.md](mdc:supabase/README.md).
- Tailwind v4 + shadcn-svelte (Nova preset, Zinc base)
- pdf-lib in Edge Functions for PDFs; Resend for email
- Vercel deployment

## Naming

- Svelte components: `PascalCase` filenames in `src/lib/components/`
- Routes: kebab-case directories
- Postgres tables: `snake_case`
- TypeScript types: `PascalCase`

## Non-negotiables

- RLS enabled on every table — fail closed. No exceptions.
- Soft delete via `deleted_at TIMESTAMPTZ` on every table except documented exceptions (`audit_log`, `module_registry`, `bible_books`, `categories`).
- Audit log is trigger-driven only. Never write to `audit_log` from app code.
- `revertible` flag is set by triggers, never by app code.
- Service role key never reaches the client — Edge Functions only.
- Two roles: `owner` (full access) and `viewer` (per-module via `user_permissions`).
- Generated DB types live in `src/lib/types/database.ts`. Regenerate with `npm run supabase:gen-types`. Never hand-write `Database` types.

## Code style

- No `any`. No default exports except SvelteKit's required ones (`+page.svelte`, `+layout.svelte`, `+page.server.ts` exports).
- Tailwind classes only — no inline `style=`.
- Extract a component when a `.svelte` file passes ~150 lines.
- Comments explain non-obvious intent, never narrate the code.
